<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">﵇</span> قال:</span> <span class="c1">"كان على <span class="c2">(طريق)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> غصن شجرة يؤذي الناس فأماطها رجل فأدخل الجنة"</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
